/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/navier-stokes/library-inbox/lin-1998-proof-architecture.md:17:Lin works in exactly the same setting as CKN: suitable weak solutions (u, p) of 3D incompressible NS on a space-time domain Q ⊆ ℝ³ × ℝ, with the local energy inequality (LEI). The parabolic cylinders Q_r(z₀) = B_r(x₀) × (t₀ − r², t₀) and scale-invariant quantities are identical to CKN.
