/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:19:- The proposed target quantities are also too easy to game. "Critical-norm transfer" or "stretching-facing spectral production" can be named without any prior reason to think they survive localization, time integration, or cancellation.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:20:- "Define in advance what would count as a usable gain" sounds disciplined, but at this stage it is fake discipline. A gain that looks usable before localization and norm conversion often disappears once commutators, phase loss, or packet overlap are included.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:31:- The kill condition uses "same effective strength," but effective strength is undefined. Is that pointwise in the symbol? averaged over orientations? after frequency summation? after localization? after time averaging? Without that definition, the gate can be passed or failed by rhetoric.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:41:- A bounded shortlist may be too aggressive because the only nontrivial leverage, if any exists, may come from a hybrid mechanism: helical selection plus localization plus scenario-specific concentration geometry. The chain is organized as though a pure triad-level discriminator should appear first and only later be translated. That ordering likely excludes the only plausible successes.
