/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:50:- Frequency-space helical statements are globally organized objects. Regularity arguments are local or at least localization-sensitive. The uncertainty-principle tax is not a detail here; it is likely the entire story.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:51:- By postponing localization until Step 4, the chain allows substantial effort to be spent on symbol-level structure that may have no physically local meaning. That is backwards. Localization should be near the front of the chain, not an after-the-fact feasibility check.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:52:- "Scenario reduction" is vague. If the scenario is meant to stand in for a blowup mechanism, it must already be fixed sharply enough that one can say what localization means and what packets or regions are supposed to dominate.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:62:- A positive output here would need more than "interesting exact NS discriminator." It would need a discriminator that survives localization, has stable sign or coercivity after summation, and still bears on a regularity-relevant quantity. The earlier steps do not build enough machinery for that.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:70:The chain treats "exact NS triad geometry differs from Tao-averaged geometry" as though this is already close to a breakthrough criterion. It is not. The missing ingredient is a mechanism that survives summation, localization, and dynamics. The chain acknowledges this only late.
