/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/planner-chains/chain-03.md:5:The harmonic-tail pressure-localization branch is dead, but it died leaving one narrow survivor: the exact pressure-Hessian and strain structure may still act on the remote-shell moments that generate the affine-or-higher harmonic tail, or on the full stretching mechanism, in a way generic harmonic regularity and Calderon-Zygmund bounds do not detect.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/planner-chains/chain-03.md:16:This chain is pressure-adjacent and tensorial. It does not reopen generic harmonic localization, and it is not just another general nonlinear rewrite. Its core objects are `nabla^2 p`, `S`, remote-shell moments, and their exact coupling.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:21:The standard "depends on algebraic structure destroyed by Tao's averaged model" is correct. But the chain uses the weaker proxy "not obviously preserved by Tao's averaged model." That is not enough. Many rewrites can look NS-specific at the identity level and still wash out once one tracks localization, projection, averaging, or frequency interactions.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:38:- positive result: must survive Tao, survive localization, survive robustness, and change closure;
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:55:- The chain never commits to which inherited architecture supplies the "target interaction." Is it the De Giorgi truncation bottleneck, a local-energy flux term, a projected pressure term, or something else? Those are not interchangeable. A candidate that helps one may be irrelevant to another.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:58:- The Tao filter is being applied before the chain has specified how the candidate enters a localized estimate. For many structures, the real question is not whether the bare identity survives averaging, but whether the exact interaction between identity, localization, and projection does.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:69:- The estimate table risks flattening the important distinctions. A rewrite can look equivalent at the headline level while generating different commutator, projector, or localization losses. If those losses are not itemized explicitly, the table will overstate "same structure" conclusions.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md:70:- The kill condition is close to tautological. Exact rewrites of NS will almost always collapse back to the same quadratic/CZ-level structure unless one also changes the testing setup or exploits additional dynamic information. If the chain only permits exact rewrites but kills anything that returns to the same structure after standard localization, then it has almost hard-coded a negative result.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/planner-chains/chain-05.md:16:This is the only chain whose main object is the localization package itself. It does not treat Lagrangian or tube-adapted coordinates as harmless setup; it audits whether the package change is the source of the apparent gain.
